 <title>Object Oriented Programming</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/training/object-oriented-programming</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-training-date-time field-type-datetime field-label-above field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Date and Time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Thursday, October 22, 2015 - &lt;div class=&quot;date-display-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-start&quot;&gt;9:00am&lt;/span&gt; to &lt;span class=&quot;date-display-end&quot;&gt;4:30pm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Trainers: Mark Ferree, Arlina Espinoza, Brian Fisher, Jaesin Mulenex and Minnur Yunusov from Chapter Three&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the move to Drupal 8 everyone who works in the PHP layer will be exposed to more and more to object­ oriented code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Come learn the basics of working with objects in PHP and how OOP can help you to write well­ structured code.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Things will kick off with the basics, keywords and syntax around using different types. This will be followed up by classes, abstract classes, and interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once we have the basic concepts in hand we will dive into namespacing, autoloading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As things draw to a close we will cover how OOP plays into application development and go over common design patterns and where you find them in use in Drupal 8.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.chapterthree.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/sponsor-logos/DCA%20Chapter3.png?itok=KfWtFkO1” alt=“Chapter Three&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above field-wrapper clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-training-location field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above field-wrapper clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Location: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;UCB Student Union Building&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-training-room field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above field-wrapper clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Room: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Tilden - USC Student Union Building&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;registrations-remaining&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;form-item form-type-item&quot;&gt;
